<br>
This won't change the way evade works very much at all.  If you think about it in a 6-person group the hate list might have 120 people on it but those 6 will be far and above the rest.  So, basically when we hit evade right now we hit 120 and at the next poke rise to at *least* number 6 (probably up to fourth).  <br>
